| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2347 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 82922a16-b3eb-5b30-84e2-a5655e4805c9"
